Nick Seraphin - RDNIS support
Gary - Phonejack ADSI (in progress)
Wasim - Hangup detect

=== HARDWARE DONORS === 
* Thanks to QuickNet Technologies for their donation of an Internet
PhoneJack and Linejack card to the project.  (http://www.quicknet.net)

